        <h2 id="pan">Pancakes</h2>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Time: 30-40 mins</li>
            <li>Serves: 2-4 people</li>
        </ul>
        
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ingredients:<br>
                        Eggs<br>
                        Sugar <br>
                        Salt<br>
                        Milk<br>
                        Flour<br>
                        Oil<br>
                        Soda
                        
                    </th>
                    <th>Quantity:<br>
                        2<br>
                        (3 table spoons) <br>
                        (1 tea spoon)<br>
                        (2 cups)<br>
                        (2 cups)<br>
                        (0.25 cup)<br>
                        (1 tea spoon)</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Beat eggs with sugar and salt until foam appears. <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 2: </strong>Add a glass of milk, beat well with a whisk, gradually add flour, constantly breaking the lumps with a whisk. <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 3: </strong>Repeat the previous step, adding the remaining glasses of milk and flour. <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 4: </strong>Pour in vegetable oil (can be replaced with melted butter).<br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 5: </strong>Extinguish the soda, add to the dough and mix well again. Leave to stand for 5-10 minutes. During this time, preheat the pan. <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 6: </strong>Fry over medium heat. As soon as bubbles appear and begin to burst, turn the pancakes over and fry for another 20 seconds. <br>
</p>

<img src = "https://www.kasandbox.org/programming-images/food/croissant.png" width = "500">
        
    
    
    <h2 id="oml">Omlette</h2>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Time: 10-20 mins</li>
            <li>Serves: 1 people</li>
        </ul>
        
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ingredients:<br>
                        Eggs<br>
                        Salt<br>
                        Milk<br>
                        Oil<br>
                        
                    </th>
                    <th>Quantity:<br>
                        2<br>
                        pinch<br>
                        half cup<br>
                        (0.25 cup)
               </th> </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <p><strong class = "st">Step 1: </strong>Beat eggs with milk and mix <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 2: </strong>Add salt <br>
        <strong>Step 3: </strong>Get ready the pan and pour oil in it. <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 4 </strong>Pour out eggs.<br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 5: </strong>Fry 5-10 mins <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 6: </strong>You can add anything you want :) <br>
</p>

<img src = "https://www.kasandbox.org/programming-images/food/fish_grilled-snapper.png" width = "500">



<h2 id="ch">Chowder</h2>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Time: 10-20 mins</li>
            <li>Serves: 1 person</li>
        </ul>
        
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ingredients:<br>
                        Flavor<br>
                        Salt<br>
                        Milk<br>
                        Sugar<br>
                        
                    </th>
                    <th>Quantity:<br>
                        1<br>
                        pinch<br>
                        a cup<br>
                        1 table spoon
               </th> </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <p><strong class = "st">Step 1: </strong>Boil milk <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 2: </strong>Add flavor <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 3: </strong>Add salt and sugar <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 4 </strong>Mix everything<br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 5: </strong>Cook 5-10 mins <br>
        <strong class = "st">Step 6: </strong>You can add anything you want :) <br>
</p>

